Title: Reporting to Mr. Anderson
Text: With valuable information gathered during my investigation, it's time to report back to Mr. Robert Anderson at the Marina Vista Caf√© and Grill. I must inform him of the progress made and the latest developments in the search for his stolen UNU Mastodon Coupe.
CompleteText: I've returned to Mr. Robert Anderson and provided a detailed report of my investigation into the stolen UNU Mastodon Coupe. While the case remains unsolved, Mr. Anderson now has a clearer picture of the situation, and we're one step closer to recovering his prized vehicle.
